et deep should provide a constant 55F temp, perfect for edible and medicinal mushrooms.&amp;nbsp; Lighting is 100% LED.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next></next>\n<prev>10509468</prev>\n<first>10504890</first>\n<last>10509560</last>\n<when>1245077120</when>\n<utime>06/15/09 05:45 PM</utime>\n</post>"}